94857.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
94857.description: When Aang and his friends go to a Fire Nation town so that Aang can witness some firebending, their plan soon goes awry when it's discovered that he is the Avatar. Fortunately, he's rescued by an individual who serves a firebending master named Jeong Jeong who has abandoned the Fire Nation, so Aang attempts to use this time to attempt to learn how to firebend. However, when the firebending master refuses to even see Aang, will Aang be able to prove he's ready to learn how to firebend despite the fact that he lacks discipline?

94858.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
94858.description: When Aang and his friends hear rumors about surviving airbenders, they decide to stop by the Northern Air Temple on their way to the North Pole to see for themselves. What they find is a bunch of people who aren't airbenders, but have mastered the art of gliding. This upsets Aang because they have been defacing the temple. However, there was one part of the temple, where nobody has been able to enter and what Aang and his friends discover inside spells oncoming conflict.

94859.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94859.description: Mr. Krabs has SpongeBob and Squidward go above and beyond the call of duty to make the first successful Krabby Patty pizza delivery. // Losing his pineapple house to parasites, SpongeBob finds himself relying on his neighbors in order to remain in his neighborhood. After disastrous stays with Patrick and Squidward, SpongeBob must move back with his parents.

94860.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94860.description: Watching their favorite show, reruns of the TV duo superhero show Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy, SpongeBob and Patrick hear that their beloved heroes are living in a nearby retirement home. // SpongeBob loses his self-confidence when an arrogant customer wrongfully claims SpongeBob forgot to put pickles on his Krabby Patty. With his perfect record now ruined, SpongeBob quits his job.

94861.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
94861.description: After an accident, Donnie finds himself slowly losing his intelligence.

94862.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
94862.description: The Turtles are baited by an unknown enemy into deadly traps.

94863.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94863.description: Tigress is forced to babysit a small child who has been separated from his parents.

94864.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94864.description: Po and Mantis visit the equivalent of an ancient Chinese Comic-Con, where Po's fanboy enthusiasm gets out of hand.

94865.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94865.description: The penguins and lemurs face off in a race. The penguins in a souped-up version of their car and the lemurs in Alice's zoo cart. Winner takes the loser's car! // Alice gives Rico a tummy-settling medicine just after he swallows a ticking time bomb.

94866.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94866.description: As the zoo starts feeding them imitation fish cakes, the penguins take matters into their own flippers and hatch a plan to hijack a fish delivery truck. // During a particularly cold day, the rats show up and challenge the penguins to a hockey match.

94867.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94867.description: SpongeBob finds Sandy Squirrel's rigorous physical training program too tough and chooses the easy way out by ordering a pair of fake "bulky arms" as seen on TV. // SpongeBob and Patrick accidentally hit Squidward with a flying shell, thinking they knocked him out. They place what is really a wax replica next to the heater, melting him.

94868.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94868.description: When Mr. Krab's daughter Pearl is stood up for her prom, SpongeBob agrees to step in. // Mr. Krabs uses the award to drive SpongeBob, but he dupes SpongeBob into believing he might break his ongoing winning streak and lose this month to Squidward.

94869.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94869.description: Fleeing from SpongeBob and Patrick's incessant noise, Squidward winds up frozen in the Krusty Krab freezer. When he finally does thaw out, he finds himself far into the future, unable to get home and actually missing SpongeBob. // SpongeBob and Sandy's incessant Karate sparring is starting to wreak havoc in the Krusty Krab. Mr. Krabs orders SpongeBob, under penalty of being fired, to cease all Karate activities.

94870.title: Nella The Princess Knight
94870.description: Nella is sent on a hair-raising rescue when Trinket is pressured into copying her friends. // Blaine serves Nella a culinary catastrophe when tries to hide his passion for cooking.

94871.title: Nella The Princess Knight
94871.description: When Olivia's sparkly ball is lost behind the bowling lanes, Nella ventures into a bowling wonderland to get it back. // When a trickster villain slips away with a treasured wedding ring, Nella must get it back before the ceremony begins.

94872.title: Bubble Guppies
94872.description: The Bubble Guppies are going on a camping trip! Grab your flashlights and gather around the campfire to make s'mores and hear about the spooky legend of Pinkfoot!

94873.title: Bubble Guppies
94873.description: Gil wants to adopt a puppy! But before he can bring the puppy home, the Bubble Guppies must learn how to take care of pets.

94874.title: Dora the Explorer
94874.description: C'mon and join the musical parade! Dora and Boots are leading a parade over the Piano Bridge and through the Swinging Gate to free the instruments that were locked up by the evil Señor Shhh!

94875.title: Dora the Explorer
94875.description: Dora and her friends are super good at hiding, especially Señor Tucán when he hides in the Rain Forest. If we can find all 8 friends, Señor Tucán promises to introduce us to his new baby toucans.

94876.title: Rusty Rivets
94876.description: While helping Chef Betty and Sammy compete for the Peachy Keen tasting contest, Rusty and Ruby must find a way to get them working together. // Ruby tries to help the monkeys at the Animal Park come up with some new performances.

94877.title: Rusty Rivets
94877.description: When Botasaur gets tired from playing, Rusty builds him a bigger battery - but with it comes a LOT more energy! // Ruby demonstrates her newest invention - the world's strongest glue - and gets all of Sparkton Hills stuck

94878.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
94878.description: Crusher and Pickle challenge Blaze and his friends to a sailboat race. But when he tries to cheat, Crusher accidentally crashes both ships onto a tropical island! Blaze and his crew must find the missing pieces of their ship so they can sail home.

94879.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
94879.description: It’s the day of the Team Truck Challenge, a race where all the trucks get to compete in teams of two! But when Crusher chooses a new partner instead of Pickle, his disappointed sidekick teams up with Blaze to prove his mettle.

94880.title: PAW Patrol
94880.description: Apollo the Super Pup comes to Adventure Bay, in Rubble’s dream. The pups must rescue their super hero! // Raimundo’s dancing hippos shake, rattle, and roll the big top down. The Paw Patrol rebuild just in time for the big show!

94881.title: PAW Patrol
94881.description: Daring Danny X takes his ambitions too far when he attempts a jump over Rattle Snake Canyon! The Paw Patrol wows with a mid-air rescue. // RoboDog’s wiring gets mixed up, and he goes on a fixing rampage around Adventure Bay!

94882.title: PAW Patrol
94882.description: A fantasy fire breathing dragon comes to life and won’t let Ryder and pups into the Lookout! Paw Patrol takes to the Air Patroller! // The Paw Patrol help three little pigs build new houses after theirs mysteriously disappear.

94883.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94883.description: When SpongeBob and Patrick think their homes have been sold, they move away - much to Squidward’s delight. // When fortune cookies start predicting the future, Plankton realizes he can twist them to his own evil schemes.

94884.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94884.description: Sandy creates the latest acorn-based food sensation, but her tree pays the price for her greed. // SpongeBob erects a community bulletin board in the Krusty Krab, but anonymous reviews posted on it lead to trouble.

94885.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94885.description: The gang heads to a food convention, but things go awry when they become stranded in the woods. // SpongeBob accidentally fibs to his pen pal, but when his friend comes to visit, he must keep the ruse going!

94886.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94886.description: When Doris the Dolphin shows up with Parker the Platypus and asks a favor of Kowalski, he instantly jumps to her rescue only to find out it’s to free her brother Francis who happens to be a “mind-jacked” Dr. Blowhole.

94887.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94887.description: Rico’s beloved doll, Miss Perky, has a new line of princess accessories! Joy! But in order for Skipper to reward the loco penguin with the new swag he must fill a marble jar (one marble in for good behavior, one marble out for bad.) How in the world is Rico supposed to behave and fill the jar when King Julien has kidnapped his dolly with the intention of marrying her?

94888.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94888.description: While repairs are being made to the noodle shop, Mr. Ping turns the training hall into a restaurant!

94889.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94889.description: When Shifu's con-man father comes back into town, Po finds himself in the middle.

94890.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
94890.description: Leo decides to sneak into Shredder's Lair alone only to face the biggest mutant threat yet.

94891.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
94891.description: After an accident, Donnie finds himself slowly losing his intelligence.

94892.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94892.description: King Neptune is celebrating his birthday at the Krusty Krab, and SpongeBob wants to make sure all his friends and family are there, including his son, Triton.

94893.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94893.description: Squidward becomes the star of his own public access TV show. // Squidward tries to sabotage SpongeBob's big dance audition.

94894.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94894.description: Mr. Krabs tries to find enough food to feed Pearl as she goes through her growth spurt. // After showering, SpongeBob gets stuck in his wringer.

94895.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94895.description: Po's visit to a famous war hero goes awry when he finds out the retired general is off his rocker.

94896.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94896.description: Po tries to help Crane get his 'mojo' back after Crane is humiliated at a charity event.

94897.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94897.description: As the vet gathers the penguins to give them a shot, Skipper's fear of needles takes over and he goes on the run. // During a solar eclipse, Phil and Mason convince the bossy Julien that the sky spirits are angry at him. He starts acting extra-nice.

94898.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94898.description: Mort is exposed to Kowalski's super-ray, and he grows super-big and strong. // Marlene gets a new roommate! At first, she's excited to have a new best friend. But her attitude changes when her roommate turns out to have some pretty disgusting habits.

94899.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
94899.description: When Raph makes a new friend in Zog, an alien Triceraton, he may have bitten off more than he can chew.

94900.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
94900.description: When the Turtles get word of the Kraang's return, they realize there is an even bigger threat coming to Earth!

94901.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94901.description: SpongeBob and Patrick become trapped in an alternate dimension where anything they draw comes to life. // SpongeBob and Patrick help Bubble Bass move out of his mother's basement.

94902.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94902.description: SpongeBob wants to be the first sponge to dive all the way up to the surface of the ocean! // When SpongeBob and Squidward accidentally let Plankton steal the secret formula, it's up to them to steal it back!

94903.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94903.description: Now that Fred's leg has healed up, SpongeBob is determined to keep it out of harm's way...no matter what! // Patrick's lemonade stand isn't doing too well...until he gets a secret ingredient from Squidward!

94904.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94904.description: When Shifu throws out his back, Po has to sit in as master of the Jade Palace.

94905.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94905.description: When kung fu is outlawed, Po turns to donning a mask to fight crime.

94906.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94906.description: The rats have been terrorizing Roger the alligator. He asks the penguins for help. Their solution: swap Roger's brain with Rico's, and let the but kicking begin! // A robot is sent to the zoo to learn the habits of lemurs before it's sent into space.

94907.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94907.description: When the penguins bring Marlene with them on a sno-cone mission in the park, she can't handle the freedom of being outside the zoo walls. // Max the cat is on the run from evil animal control Officer X, and he comes to the penguins for help.

94908.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
94908.description: When Aang tries to find the north pole, he is found by the north pole waterbenders instead. When they are taken there, Aang and Katara are eager to find a waterbending master, only to find that girls are not allowed to learn waterbending. Katara decides to show everyone what she can do. Meanwhile, Sokka falls in love with the tribe's princess.

94909.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
94909.description: Zhao begins to launch his attack against the Northern Water Tribe. As the walls of the besieged city begin to fall, the Avatar taps into the spirit world and seeks the help of one of the oldest spirits, in hopes of saving one of the most prominent areas of the world. Can Aang combine forces with the spirits and save the Northern Water Tribe?

94910.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94910.description: When The Krusty Krab runs out of mustard, Mr. Krabs sends SpongeBob, Patrick and Squidward to dig up some more! // SpongeBob and Sandy have to collect Krabby Patty ingredients, but Plankton is following their every step.

94911.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94911.description: Mr. Krabs hires Squidward to babysit Pearl for the night, but she just wants to sneak out to a cool teen party! // After spilling a milkshake during a delivery, SpongeBob vows to return and clean the entire building!

94912.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94912.description: Plankton tells Patrick he's his conscience so he can convince the wooden-headed star to steal him a Krabby Patty. // When Mr. Krabs puts in an open kitchen, SpongeBob gets stage fright and has to invent a new persona.

94913.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
94913.description: When the Turtles get word of the Kraang's return, they realize there is an even bigger threat coming to Earth!

94914.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
94914.description: When Shredder teams with the Kraang to receive a batch of mutagen, the Turtles' problems only get worse-even putting their friendship with April at stake.

94915.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94915.description: When two Croc Bandits have a spat, it's up to Po and Mr. Ping to set things right.

94916.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
94916.description: In an attempt to get out of training, Po buys some enchanted shoes that will heighten his kung fu abilities. Unfortunately for Po, the magical shoes are evil and will soon put him and all those around him in great danger.

94917.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94917.description: When Rico gets a freaky fortune from his cookie, he initially ignores it. Julien sets out to make Rico's fortune come true. // A female chimp named Lulu arrives at the zoo for a short stay, and Phil is smitten. Unfortunately, Lulu falls for Mason.

94918.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94918.description: On watch-duty, Private sees a terrifying Skorka: a sky orca whale. No one believes it exists, so Private sets out to battle the Sorka on his own. // When the penguins are interrupted mid-operation by a nosey scientist, they leave the zoo in danger.

94919.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
94919.description: A little girl loses her doll at the zoo, and Rico gives up his own doll to replace it. Private assures Rico that his good deed will come back to him. // When a raccoon shows up and starts stealing from the zoo animals, the penguins jump into action.

94920.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94920.description: Plankton hasn't tried to steal the secret formula in a while...and that's making Mr. Krabs nervous! // When Patrick discovers the pineapple's library, SpongeBob introduces him to the wonderful world of book learning!

94921.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
94921.description: Plankton goes to jail, but the secret formula is taken as evidence! SpongeBob and Mr. Krabs plot to get it back. // Sandy struggles to build a ship-in-a-bottle before a big contest, so SpongeBob calls in a little extra help.
